author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Capital & Counties Says ‍Contracts Exchanged On 49 Units At Lillie Square​
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Capital & Counties Properties Plc :
* ‍CONTRACTS EXCHANGED ON 49 UNITS AT LILLIE SQUARE​ * ‍EXCHANGED CONTRACTS WITH INTERNATIONAL INVESTOR FOR SALE OF 49 APARTMENTS AND 31 PARKING SPACES AT ‘9 LILLIE SQUARE’​
* ‍TOTAL SALE CONSIDERATION IS APPROXIMATELY £66 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
